                </div>
                <div class="service-text">
                    <h3 class="h2">Electrical Repairs</h3>
                    <p>Our team can quickly diagnose and repair any electrical issues in your home or business. We offer comprehensive repair services for all types of electrical systems, including wiring, outlets, and circuit breakers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-block service-item" data-aos="fade-up">
