                    <p>Regular maintenance is essential to keep your electrical systems running smoothly and prevent potential issues. We offer ongoing maintenance services to keep your electrical systems in optimal condition and reduce the risk of breakdowns and failures.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-block service-item" data-aos="fade-up">
                <div class="service-icon">
                    <!-- <i class="icon-earth"></i> -->
                    <!-- <img src="/images/icons/schematics@64x64_border.png"> -->
                    <Icon icon="schematic" width={iconWidth}>
                </div>
                <div class="service-text">
                    <h3 class="h2">Electrical Upgrades</h3>
                    <p>If your electrical system is outdated or needs an upgrade, we can help. Our team can assess your current system and recommend upgrades to improve its efficiency, safety, and performance.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-block service-item" data-aos="fade-up">
                <div class="service-icon">
                    <!-- <i class="icon-cube"></i> -->
                    <!-- <img src="/images/icons/voltmter@64x64_border.png"> -->
                    <Icon icon="voltmeter" width={iconWidth}>
                </div>
                <div class="service-text">
                    <h3 class="h2">Electrical Testing</h3>
                    <p>We provide thorough electrical safety inspections to identify potential hazards and ensure that your electrical system is up to code and compliant with regulations.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-block service-item" data-aos="fade-up">
                <div class="service-icon">
                    <!-- <img src="/images/icons/repairs@64x64_border.png"> -->
                    <Icon icon="repair" width={iconWidth}>
                </div>
                <div class="service-text">
                    <h3 class="h2">Emergency Electrical Services</h3>
                    <p>We offer emergency electrical services to quickly respond to electrical emergencies. Our team of electricians is equipped to handle any urgent issue, from power outages to tripping circuit breakers, to help you get your electrical system up and running again.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

